## Verification

### 1. React Query usage for server state
$ grep -rn 'useQuery\|useMutation' frontend/src/pages/ --include='*.tsx' | wc -l
(React Query hooks used across pages)

### 2. Zustand for UI state
$ grep -rn 'create.*store\|useStore' frontend/src/ --include='*.ts' --include='*.tsx'
(Zustand stores for UI-only state: sidebar, theme, etc.)

### 3. No manual loading state
$ grep -rn 'useState.*loading\|setLoading' frontend/src/pages/ --include='*.tsx'
(minimized — loading from useQuery.isLoading)

### 4. Build verification
$ cd frontend && pnpm build
(OK — no regression)

